title: The 20YA | Post-Event Release Schedule
body_text: I promised plenty of never-before-recorded clips from the 20YA so be sure to check out this exciting list of release dates! I'd like to thank best bud Mike Edwards and his brother Jon for all the incredible footage. The first one highlighting the event introduction and opening rush will be released this Saturday, 10/11.
